    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "To be clear, I'm not sure that we *should* support it.\r\n\r\nCurrently EA.take always returns an `ExtensionArray`. That's a nice piece of knowledge to rely on. I'd rather not have to litter all call-sites of EA.take with checks for whether indices is a scalar or not."
